title: Week 15 Tuesday Night Football Recap: Eagles beat depleted WFT, Rams top Seahawks (Football 12/22)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech react to Tuesday football. First they focus on the Eagles victory over Washington and which NFC team will secure the #7 seed. Then, they shift focus to the Rams win over the Seahawks, commenting on the end of Seattle's season and if LA can win the NFC West. 

(6:00) Eagles-WFT
(34:00) Rams-Seahawks
